name: Alice Aufray
introduction: Alice Aufray (born 27 September 1992 in Hamburg, Germany) is a German fashion model, known for her appearances in magazines like Kneon, METAL and Cosmopolitan. She is also an actress who made her film debut in the 2014 French comedy Un Village Presque Parfait. She originally signed with the Nathalie Agency in 2010. She made back-to-back covers for Cosmopolitan France in July and August 2012. ... (more)
